sources.title: Film Noir 7 C Not Wanted 281949 Ida Lupino 29 Sally Forrest 2 C Keefe Brasselle
sources.description: After a romantic fling with a nightclub pianist, a young woman discovers that she's pregnant. When the father abandons her, she faces a difficult choice: should she keep her baby, or give it up for adoption? All the while her shame keeps her from the man who truly loves her...
